The servlet 2.5 spec requires the following API signature for
javax/servlet/jsp/tagext/TagInfo.java

public static final String BODY_CONTENT_TAG_DEPENDENT = "tagdependent";
public static final String BODY_CONTENT_EMPTY = "empty";
public static final String BODY_CONTENT_SCRIPTLESS = "scriptless";

See:
http://java.sun.com/javaee/5/docs/api/constant-values.html#javax.servlet
